    <title>dns验证方式使用letsencrypt证书</title>
    <link href="https://www.chengchangqin.com/2018/02/01/3-letsencrypt-acme-sh/"/>
    <id>https://www.chengchangqin.com/2018/02/01/3-letsencrypt-acme-sh/</id>
    <published>2018-02-01T02:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-02-04T12:54:00.218Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>全站HTTPS支持<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="安装acme-sh"><a href="#安装acme-sh" class="headerlink" title="安装acme.sh"></a>安装acme.sh</h2><p>自动安装到~/.acme.sh/文件夹,<br>会创建crontab，检测证书是否过期<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">curl  https://get.acme.sh | sh</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>开启脚本自动更新<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">acme.sh --upgrade --auto-upgrade</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><h2 id="生成证书"><a href="#生成证书" class="headerlink" title="生成证书"></a>生成证书</h2><p>使用阿里云解析api自动添加txt解析记录<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> Ali_Key=<span class="string">"***"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> Ali_Secret=<span class="string">"***"</span></div><div class="line">acme.sh --issue --dns dns_ali -d example.com</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>解析生效后重新生成证书<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">acme.sh --renew -d example.com</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><h2 id="安装证书"><a href="#安装证书" class="headerlink" title="安装证书"></a>安装证书</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">acme.sh --installcert -d example.com   \</div><div class="line">    --key-file /home/&lt;id&gt;/letsencrypt/&lt;id&gt;.key \</div><div class="line">    --fullchain-file /home/&lt;id&gt;/letsencrypt/&lt;id&gt;.cer \</div><div class="line">    --reloadcmd <span class="string">"service nginx force-reload"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="nginx更改配置"><a href="#nginx更改配置" class="headerlink" title="nginx更改配置"></a>nginx更改配置</h2><ul><li>ssl_certificate 对应 fullchain-file</li><li>ssl_certificate_key 对应 –key-file</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">service nginx reload</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h2><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/Neilpang/acme.sh" target="_blank" rel="external">acme.sh</a></li><li><a href="https://www.ssllabs.com" target="_blank" rel="external">ssllabs</a></li><li><a href="https://tool.lu/dns/index.html" target="_blank" rel="external">dns查询</a></li><li><a href="https://ak-console.aliyun.com/#/accesskey" target="_blank" rel="external">aliyun密钥</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
