    <title>开放地图上标注公司信息</title>
    <link href="https://www.chengchangqin.com/2017/10/12/2-baidu-map-label/"/>
    <id>https://www.chengchangqin.com/2017/10/12/2-baidu-map-label/</id>
    <published>2017-10-12T12:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-02-04T12:53:48.668Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>利用百度的开放地图标注公司信息<br>这里记录一下过程<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="申请百度地图API密钥"><a href="#申请百度地图API密钥" class="headerlink" title="申请百度地图API密钥"></a>申请百度地图API密钥</h2><p><a href="http://lbsyun.baidu.com/apiconsole/key" target="_blank" rel="external">注册</a><br><a href="http://lbsyun.baidu.com/jsdemo.htm" target="_blank" rel="external">示例</a></p><h2 id="提取百度坐标"><a href="#提取百度坐标" class="headerlink" title="提取百度坐标"></a>提取百度坐标</h2><p>利用百度地图工具<a href="http://api.map.baidu.com/lbsapi/getpoint/index.html" target="_blank" rel="external">拾取坐标系统</a></p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> point1 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Point(<span class="number">116.156346</span>,<span class="number">28.34574</span>);<span class="comment">//进贤养护所</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> point2 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Point(<span class="number">116.035085</span>,<span class="number">28.805284</span>);<span class="comment">//南新养护站</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> point3 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Point(<span class="number">116.284881</span>,<span class="number">28.048271</span>);<span class="comment">//临川养护站</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> point4 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Point(<span class="number">115.8309</span>,<span class="number">27.99897</span>);<span class="comment">//洛市养护站</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> point5 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Point(<span class="number">116.19117</span>,<span class="number">27.589782</span>);<span class="comment">//宜黄养护站</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> point6 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Point(<span class="number">115.290875</span>,<span class="number">27.224466</span>);<span class="comment">//乌江养护站</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="初始化地图"><a href="#初始化地图" class="headerlink" title="初始化地图"></a>初始化地图</h2><p>默认显示全部点</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> map = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Map(<span class="string">"allmap"</span>, &#123;<span class="attr">minZoom</span>:<span class="number">9</span>,<span class="attr">maxZoom</span>:<span class="number">16</span>&#125;);</div><div class="line">map.centerAndZoom(point1,<span class="number">9</span>);</div><div class="line">map.enableScrollWheelZoom(<span class="literal">true</span>);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加自定义控件"><a href="#添加自定义控件" class="headerlink" title="添加自定义控件"></a>添加自定义控件</h2><p>左上角添加控件，可返回初始化页面</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">ZoomControl</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">this</span>.defaultAnchor = BMAP_ANCHOR_TOP_LEFT;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">this</span>.defaultOffset = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Size(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">10</span>);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">ZoomControl.prototype = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Control();</div><div class="line">ZoomControl.prototype.initialize = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">map</span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> div = <span class="built_in">document</span>.createElement(<span class="string">"div"</span>);</div><div class="line">    div.appendChild(<span class="built_in">document</span>.createTextNode(<span class="string">"进贤养护所"</span>));</div><div class="line">    <span class="comment">// 设置样式</span></div><div class="line">    div.style.cursor = <span class="string">"pointer"</span>;</div><div class="line">    div.style.border = <span class="string">"2px solid white"</span>;</div><div class="line">    div.style.color = <span class="string">"#FFFFFF"</span>;</div><div class="line">    div.style.backgroundColor = <span class="string">"red"</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="comment">// 绑定事件</span></div><div class="line">    div.onclick = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">e</span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">        map.centerAndZoom(point1,<span class="number">9</span>);</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">    <span class="comment">// 添加DOM元素到地图中</span></div><div class="line">    map.getContainer().appendChild(div);</div><div class="line">    <span class="comment">// 将DOM元素返回</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> div;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">// 创建控件</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> myZoomCtrl = <span class="keyword">new</span> ZoomControl();</div><div class="line">map.addControl(myZoomCtrl);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加点标注"><a href="#添加点标注" class="headerlink" title="添加点标注"></a>添加点标注</h2><p>将所站标注出来，单击可放大页面<br>可显示图文组合的信息窗口</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">attribute</span>(<span class="params">e</span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> p = e.target;</div><div class="line">    map.centerAndZoom(p.getPosition(),<span class="number">16</span>);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> marker1 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Marker(point1);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> label1= <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Label(<span class="string">"进贤养护所"</span>,&#123;<span class="attr">offset</span>:<span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Size(<span class="number">20</span>,<span class="number">-10</span>)&#125;);</div><div class="line">marker1.setLabel(label1);</div><div class="line">marker1.setAnimation(BMAP_ANIMATION_BOUNCE); <span class="comment">//跳动的动画</span></div><div class="line">marker1.addEventListener(<span class="string">"click"</span>,<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    map.centerAndZoom(point1,<span class="number">16</span>);</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> content1 = </div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"&lt;h4 style='margin:0 0 5px 0;padding:0.2em 0'&gt;进贤养护所&lt;/h4&gt;"</span> + </div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"&lt;img style='float:right;margin:4px' id='imgDemo'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="string">        src='https://ccq.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/images/jxyhs-min.jpg'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="string">        width='139' height='104' title='进贤养护所'/&gt;"</span> + </div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"&lt;p style='margin:0;line-height:1.5;font-size:13px'&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="string">        地址：江西省进贤县沥背陈家&lt;/p&gt;"</span> + <span class="string">"&lt;/div&gt;"</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> infoWindow = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.InfoWindow(content1);</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">this</span>.openInfoWindow(infoWindow);</div><div class="line">    <span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">'imgDemo'</span>).onload = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">        infoWindow.redraw(); </div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div><div class="line">map.addOverlay(marker1);<span class="comment">//添加点1</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> marker2 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Marker(point2);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> label2 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Label(<span class="string">"南新养护站"</span>,&#123;<span class="attr">offset</span>:<span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Size(<span class="number">20</span>,<span class="number">-10</span>)&#125;);</div><div class="line">marker2.setLabel(label2);</div><div class="line">marker2.addEventListener(<span class="string">"click"</span>,attribute);</div><div class="line">map.addOverlay(marker2);<span class="comment">//添加点2</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> marker3 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Marker(point3);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> label3 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Label(<span class="string">"临川养护站"</span>,&#123;<span class="attr">offset</span>:<span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Size(<span class="number">20</span>,<span class="number">-10</span>)&#125;);</div><div class="line">marker3.setLabel(label3);</div><div class="line">marker3.addEventListener(<span class="string">"click"</span>,attribute);</div><div class="line">map.addOverlay(marker3);<span class="comment">//添加点3</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> marker4 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Marker(point4);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> label4 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Label(<span class="string">"洛市养护站"</span>,&#123;<span class="attr">offset</span>:<span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Size(<span class="number">20</span>,<span class="number">-10</span>)&#125;);</div><div class="line">marker4.setLabel(label4);</div><div class="line">marker4.addEventListener(<span class="string">"click"</span>,attribute);</div><div class="line">map.addOverlay(marker4);<span class="comment">//添加点4</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> marker5 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Marker(point5);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> label5 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Label(<span class="string">"宜黄养护站"</span>,&#123;<span class="attr">offset</span>:<span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Size(<span class="number">20</span>,<span class="number">-10</span>)&#125;);</div><div class="line">marker5.setLabel(label5);</div><div class="line">marker5.addEventListener(<span class="string">"click"</span>,attribute);</div><div class="line">map.addOverlay(marker5);<span class="comment">//添加点5</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> marker6 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Marker(point6);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> label6 = <span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Label(<span class="string">"乌江养护站"</span>,&#123;<span class="attr">offset</span>:<span class="keyword">new</span> BMap.Size(<span class="number">20</span>,<span class="number">-10</span>)&#125;);</div><div class="line">marker6.setLabel(label6);</div><div class="line">marker6.addEventListener(<span class="string">"click"</span>,attribute);</div><div class="line">map.addOverlay(marker6);<span class="comment">//添加点6</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="效果"><a href="#效果" class="headerlink" title="效果"></a>效果</h2><iframe src="https://www.chengchangqin.com/jxyhs-baidu-demo.html" frameborder="0" height="500" width="400" style="border:0"></iframe>]]></content>
    
