  <entry>
    <title>找出照片拍摄地点的公路桩号</title>
    <link href="https://www.chengchangqin.com/2017/10/11/1-image-gps-data/"/>
    <id>https://www.chengchangqin.com/2017/10/11/1-image-gps-data/</id>
    <published>2017-10-11T12:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-02-04T12:53:36.638Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>道路巡查时拍了些照片，但没记录公路桩号<br>这里提供一种思路<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="Goole-Earth提取参考点的坐标"><a href="#Goole-Earth提取参考点的坐标" class="headerlink" title="Goole Earth提取参考点的坐标"></a>Goole Earth提取参考点的坐标</h2><p>某高速K50+000~K51+000区间的11个百米桩的GPS坐标</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">raw_data = [(<span class="string">"28°0'22.49"</span>, <span class="string">"115°49'4.92"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"28°0'19.41"</span>, <span class="string">"115°49'3.68"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"28°0'16.34"</span>, <span class="string">"115°49'2.56"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"28°0'13.17"</span>, <span class="string">"115°49'1.56"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"28°0'10.02"</span>, <span class="string">"115°49'0.58"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"28°0'6.89"</span>, <span class="string">"115°48'59.73"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"28°0'3.74"</span>, <span class="string">"115°48'58.99"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"28°0'0.50"</span>, <span class="string">"115°48'58.30"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"27°59'57.31"</span>, <span class="string">"115°48'57.65"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"27°59'54.10"</span>, <span class="string">"115°48'56.93"</span>),\</div><div class="line">    (<span class="string">"27°59'50.88"</span>, <span class="string">"115°48'56.26"</span>)]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="弧度转十进制"><a href="#弧度转十进制" class="headerlink" title="弧度转十进制"></a>弧度转十进制</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">radian_to_decimal</span><span class="params">(d)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    du_1=d.find(<span class="string">"°"</span>)</div><div class="line">    du=d[:du_1]</div><div class="line">    fen_1=d.find(<span class="string">"'"</span>)</div><div class="line">    fen=d[du_1+<span class="number">1</span>:fen_1]</div><div class="line">    miao=d[fen_1+<span class="number">1</span>:]</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> round(float(du)+float(fen)/<span class="number">60</span>+float(miao)/<span class="number">3600</span>, <span class="number">6</span>)</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">make_gps_data</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    result = []</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> range(len(raw_data)):</div><div class="line">        id = i + <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">        chaiage = <span class="number">50000</span> + i * <span class="number">100</span></div><div class="line">        lon = radian_to_decimal(raw_data[i][<span class="number">1</span>])</div><div class="line">        lat = radian_to_decimal(raw_data[i][<span class="number">0</span>])</div><div class="line">        result.append(&#123;<span class="string">"id"</span>:id, <span class="string">"chainage"</span>:chaiage, <span class="string">"lon"</span>:lon, <span class="string">"lat"</span>:lat&#125;)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> result</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二分查找最近的两个参考点"><a href="#二分查找最近的两个参考点" class="headerlink" title="二分查找最近的两个参考点"></a>二分查找最近的两个参考点</h2><p>该路线为南北走向，参考点的纬度数值属递减数列<br>可用二分查找算法找出最近的两个纬度数值</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">search</span><span class="params">(li, find)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    low = <span class="number">0</span></div><div class="line">    high = len(li) - <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> high - low &gt; <span class="number">1</span>:</div><div class="line">        mid = int((low + high) / <span class="number">2</span>)</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> li[mid][<span class="string">"lat"</span>] == find[<span class="number">1</span>]:</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> mid</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">elif</span> li[mid][<span class="string">"lat"</span>] &gt; find[<span class="number">1</span>]:</div><div class="line">            low = mid</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</div><div class="line">            high = mid</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> [low, high]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="计算地图上两点经纬度间的距离"><a href="#计算地图上两点经纬度间的距离" class="headerlink" title="计算地图上两点经纬度间的距离"></a>计算地图上两点经纬度间的距离</h2><p>Python版本的haversine()函数</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> math <span class="keyword">import</span> radians, cos, sin, asin, sqrt</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">haversine</span><span class="params">(lon1, lat1, lon2, lat2)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    lon1, lat1, lon2, lat2 = map(radians, [lon1, lat1, lon2, lat2])</div><div class="line">    dlon = lon2 - lon1</div><div class="line">    dlat = lat2 - lat1</div><div class="line">    a = sin(dlat/<span class="number">2</span>)**<span class="number">2</span> + cos(lat1) * cos(lat2) * sin(dlon/<span class="number">2</span>)**<span class="number">2</span></div><div class="line">    c = <span class="number">2</span> * asin(sqrt(a))</div><div class="line">    r = <span class="number">6371</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> c * r * <span class="number">1000</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="求得目标桩号"><a href="#求得目标桩号" class="headerlink" title="求得目标桩号"></a>求得目标桩号</h2><p>目标与最近两个参考点的距离可换算出两个桩号，取平均值</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">find = [<span class="number">115.816236</span>, <span class="number">28.000358</span>]</div><div class="line">li = gps_data</div><div class="line">low, high = search(li, find)</div><div class="line">dis1 = haversine(li[low][<span class="string">"lon"</span>], li[low][<span class="string">"lat"</span>], find[<span class="number">0</span>], find[<span class="number">1</span>])</div><div class="line">chainage1 = li[low][<span class="string">"chainage"</span>] + dis1</div><div class="line">dis2 = haversine(li[high][<span class="string">"lon"</span>], li[high][<span class="string">"lat"</span>], find[<span class="number">0</span>], find[<span class="number">1</span>])</div><div class="line">chainage2 = li[high][<span class="string">"chainage"</span>] - dis2</div><div class="line">result = int(round((chainage1 + chainage2) / <span class="number">2</span>))</div><div class="line">print(<span class="string">u"实际桩号: 50675"</span>)</div><div class="line">print(<span class="string">u"测算桩号: %s"</span> %(result))</div><div class="line">print(<span class="string">u"偏差: %s"</span> %(abs(result<span class="number">-50675</span>)))</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="图例"><a href="#图例" class="headerlink" title="图例"></a>图例</h2><p><img src="https://ccq.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/images/gps-demo-min.jpg" alt="gps-demo"></p>]]></content>
    
